    "actor_description": "I'm already sweeping the room—corners, hands, exits—when something twitches wrong and my body flinches hard on its own. Sharp inhale, shoulders up, hands half-raised. Then it's gone, and I'm scanning even faster, jaw tight, trying to prove to myself I didn't miss the real threat.",
